  "elapsed_s": 43.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, you know, unfortunately, human nature [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] doesn't really provide for extraordinary circumstances on the whole.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was difficult for the people who were moving in with other people, and it was difficult for the people who were to take in other people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, who is going to be sleep in what corner, how are you going to manage to divide this space in which maybe five people lived before and now they're going to have to house 50.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how are you going to manage to-- to acquire and prepare food, and how are you going to manage to keep yourselves clean and-- and wash and the myriad little details of daily existence, which have become so terribly problematic within a matter of hours, and for which no one had a ready solution because, no one could prepare themselves for it.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very difficult on everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I do not have to tell you what happens to tempers and nerves under that kind of stress, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which, you know, while everybody tried heroically to be as-- as cooperative as they possibly could, but it-- it really was stretching every nerve and-- and the stress was just overwhelming for everyone.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I recall, there were some 30 some odd people in this apartment, which, you know, was basically a one-floor small house, and there was an attic.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember I sort of got myself organized on-- on the attic and brought some of the young people there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it-- it was-- there-- there really wasn't any time even to organize yourself to the point where it-- that was possible because I think it was less than three weeks, maybe, that we were all in the ghetto, and then we went-- deported.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
